  <summary date="2019-10-23T14:34:51Z" status="Introduced in Senate">New Home Energy Efficiency Act

This bill reinstates and extends the new home energy efficiency tax credit through 2022. It also increases to $2,500 in 2021 and through 2022, the amount of such credit for new homes meeting the revised energy efficiency standards set forth in the bill.</summary>
